balance%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%26quot%3B%20Luddington%20told%20Parents%2C%20adding%20she%20focuses%20on%20doing%20her%20best%20in%20each%20role%20depending%20on%20the%20day.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BTo%20take%20the%20pressure%20off%2C%20I'll%20be%20like%2C%20'You%20know%20what%3F%20Today%20I'm%20probably%20going%20to%20be%20better%20at%20my%20job%20than%20I%20am%20at%20parenting%20because%20I'm%20on%20set%20all%20day.%20But%20tomorrow%20I'm%20off%20and%20I%20can%20be%20a%20better%20parent%2C'%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20%26quot%3BLetting%20go%20of%20that%20need%20to%20be%20perfectly%20balanced%20all%20the%20time%20has%20been%20very%20freeing%20for%20me.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELuddington%20has%20played%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffacts-about-greys-anatomy-2018-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EDr.%20Jo%20Wilson%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20the%20hit%20medical%20drama%20since%202012.%20She%3Cmark%20data-color%3D%5C%22rgba(0%2C%200%2C%200%2C%200)%5C%22%3E%20has%20two%20kids%20with%20her%20husband%2C%20%26quot%3B13%20Reasons%20Why%26quot%3B%20actor%20Matthew%20Alan.%3C%2Fmark%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20it%20comes%20to%20her%20two%20kids%2C%20ages%208%20and%205%2C%20Luddington%20says%20that%20having%20space%20is%20sometimes%20the%20secret%20to%20harmony.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey%20want%20to%20play%20together%20and%20they%20want%20to%20be%20up%20against%20us%20%E2%80%94%20but%20they%20don't%20realize%20that%20they%20need%20time%20by%20themselves%2C%26quot%3B%20Luddington%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20times%2C%20she%20and%20her%20husband%20will%20split%20the%20kids%20up%2C%20sending%20one%20out%20to%20play%20and%20the%20other%20to%20the%20room%2C%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey%20need%20that%20separation%20because%20they%20will%20be%20up%20in%20each%20other's%20business%20the%20entire%20day%20and%20drive%20each%20other%20%E2%80%94%20and%20us%20%E2%80%94%20crazy.%20Then%20they%20can%20appreciate%20the%20time%20they%20spend%20with%20us%20and%20each%20other%2C%26quot%3B%20Luddington%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20representative%20for%20Luddington%20did%20not%20immediately%20respond%20to%20a%20request%20for%20comment%20sent%20by%20Business%20Insider%20outside%20regular%20hours.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20a%202023%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.newbeauty.com%2Fcamilla-luddington-interview%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Einterview%20with%20NewBeauty%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Luddington%20said%20she's%20%26quot%3Blucky%26quot%3B%20to%20be%20on%20a%20show%20with%20a%20big%20cast%20that%20doesn't%20require%20her%20on%20set%20daily.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBut%20there%20are%20days%20that%20go%20by%20where%20I've%20worked%20a%20couple%20of%2012-hour%20days%20and%20I%20haven't%20seen%20my%20kids%20in%20three%20days.%20And%20that's%20hard.%20So%20the%20days%20that%20I%20have%20time%20off%2C%20I%20try%20to%20give%20them%20as%20much%20of%20my%20attention%20as%20I%20possibly%20can%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELuddington%20joins%20a%20list%20of%20female%20actors%20who've%20opened%20up%20about%20juggling%20work%20and%20parenting%20in%20Hollywood.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20to%20The%20Times%20in%20November%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fkeira-knightley-choose-between-career-motherhood-children-work-2024-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EKeira%20Knightley%3C%2Fa%3E%20said%20having%20kids%20meant%20putting%20her%20career%20on%20the%20back%20burner.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20couldn't%20go%20job%20to%20job%20%5Babroad%5D%20now.%20It%20wouldn't%20be%20in%20any%20way%20fair%20on%20them%2C%20and%20I%20wouldn't%20want%20to%2C%26quot%3B%20Knightley%20said.%20%26quot%3BI've%20chosen%20to%20have%20children%2C%20I%20want%20to%20bring%20them%20up%2C%20so%20I've%20had%20to%20take%20a%20major%20step%20back.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20May%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmichelle-williams-cant-be-equally-good-parenting-work-motherhood-2025-5%5C%22%2