%3D%5C%22wp-image-490417%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EAll%20four%20students%20worked%20equally%20hard%20to%20make%20sure%20that%20the%20device%20was%20a%20success%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20withstand%20the%20often%20harsh%20and%20unpredictable%20field%20conditions%20in%20Indian%20agriculture%2C%20the%20team%20focused%20on%20making%20the%20device%20robust.%20It%20includes%20a%20waterproof%20casing%20and%20a%20lithium%20polymer%20(LiPo)%20battery%20that%20can%20last%20through%20multiple%20uses%2C%20making%20it%20both%20durable%20and%20farmer-friendly.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EThe%20right%20fertiliser%2C%20at%20the%20right%20time%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEqually%20critical%20to%20the%20project%20is%20the%20Agroww%20app%2C%20designed%20using%20FlutterFlow.%20This%20app%20serves%20as%20the%20brain%20behind%20the%20device%2C%20offering%20farmers%20a%20streamlined%20and%20bilingual%20interface%20in%20both%20English%20and%20Hindi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CFarmers%20do%20not%20have%20time%20to%20figure%20out%20complex%20apps%20or%20scroll%20through%20confusing%20jargon%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Gaurvica%2C%20who%20designs%20the%20app%E2%80%99s%20interface%20and%20backend%20logic.%20%E2%80%9CIt%20needs%20to%20be%20fast%2C%20simple%2C%20and%20informative.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F08%2FBlue-and-Yellow-Modern-Business-Workshop-Facebook-Ad-2025-08-22T080413.725_11zon-1755830098.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Mati%20Rakshak%20is%20a%20sleek%2C%20handheld%20tool%20that%20analyses%20soil%20nutrients%20in%20real%20time%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F08%2FBlue-and-Yellow-Mode