%3E%2C%20including%20the%20zoo%2C%20the%20beach%2C%20and%20lots%20of%20outdoor%20breaks%20in%20our%20front%20and%20backyard.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%221bdc7641-75ce-45e5-99cc-d6637d7d5bcf%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cstrong%3EI%20saw%20the%20advantages%20of%20a%20slower-paced%20schedule%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20outside%20time%20we%20were%20both%20experiencing%20felt%20healthier%20than%20being%20inside%20most%20of%20the%20day%20at%20school.%20I%20also%20liked%20that%20we%20could%20easily%20make%20adjustments%20in%20our%20schedule%20and%20fit%20in%20lots%20of%20breaks.%20As%20both%20a%20teacher%20and%20a%20mother%2C%20I%20think%20the%20traditional%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fschool-spirit-days-benefits-community-students-2023-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ein-person%20school%20day%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20can%20be%20a%20lot%20of%20work.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EMy%20favorite%20part%20about%20homeschooling%20was%20that%20my%20son%20had%20more%20space%20to%20explore%20his%20interests.%20I%20always%20found%20that%20my%20students%20did%20best%20when%20the%20subject%20matter%20involved%20something%20that%20intrigued%20them.%20One%20way%20I%20tried%20to%20make%20homeschooling%20advantageous%20was%20by%20supporting%20the%20topics%20my%20son%20was%20curious%20about.%20If%20he%20was%20really%20interested%20in%20animals%20for%20example%2C%20then%20I%20scheduled%20visits%20to%20the%20zoo%20and%20planned%20trips%20to%20the%20library%20to%20check%20out%20books%20on%20specific%20animals.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%229da68a4a-63c4-4a35-ba3a-41636c3b820e%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cstrong%3EThere%20were%20also%20downsides%20to%20our%20new%20way%20of%20life%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20the%20long%20term%2C%20I%20knew%20that%20independence%20from%20each%20other%20was%20better%20for%20our%20relationship.%20I