at%20as%20a%20passenger%3B%20no%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftesla-vs-waymo-full-self-driving-fsd-robotaxi-lidar-cameras-2025-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ehuman%20supervision%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20required.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20is%20mind%20off%2C%20eyes%20off%2C%20hands%20off%2C%26quot%3B%20Hugo%20Fozzati%2C%20Tensor's%20chief%20business%20officer%2C%20said%20in%20an%20interview.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20car's%20SAE%20Level%204%20driving%20system%20%E2%80%94%20a%20classification%20that%20indicates%20it%20can%20drive%20without%20human%20supervision%20%E2%80%94%20can%20only%20be%20activated%20in%20%26quot%3Bapproved%26quot%3B%20zones%20or%20within%20the%20%26quot%3Boperational%20design%20domains%26quot%3B%20(ODD)%2C%20Fozzati%20said%20%E2%80%94%20basically%20geofences%2C%20akin%20to%20those%20that%20corral%20robotaxis%20like%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwaymo%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EAlphabet's%20Waymo%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSo%20when%20it's%20in%20our%20ODD%2C%20you're%20free%20to%20basically%20press%20the%20Level%204%20mode%20and%20then%20the%20steering%20wheel%20folds%20away%2C%20the%20pedal%20folds%20away%2C%20and%20that's%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%20data-script%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20data-styles%3D%5C%22default-width%5C%22%20data-embed-type%3D%5C%22custom%5C%22%20data-type%3D%5C%22embed%5C%22%3E%3Ciframe%20referrerpolicy%3D%5C%22strict-origin-when-cross-origin%5C%22%20allowfullscreen%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fembed%2FwcLXmTFPyYU%3Fsi%3D1fhjThlCoq-VftuR%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22560%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22YouTube%20video%20player%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22315%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cp%3EFozzati%20said%20once%20the%20autonomous%20driving%20feature%20is%20activated%2C%20Tensor%20takes%20full%20responsibility%20for%20what%20happens%20on%20the%20road.%20So%20if%20the%20car%20gets%20into%20a%20collision%2C%20Tensor%20could%20be%20on%20t