es%20face%20a%20patchwork%20of%20state-by-state%20laws.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%226961%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Tensor%20Robocar%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F68b36373194a2d49b8af80d9%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%225221%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EUsers%20of%20Tensor%20Robocar%20will%20be%20able%20to%20interact%20with%20the%20vehicle%20through%20conversational%20voice%20commands.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20Tensor%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EStarting%20price%20is%20TBD.%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EThe%20car%20has%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwaymo-robotaxi-lidar-sensor-versus-cameras-vision-only-2025-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Elot%20of%20sensors%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20add%20to%20its%20weight%20and%2C%20most%20likely%2C%20to%20its%20price%3A%2037%20cameras%2C%205%20lidars%2C%2011%20radars%2C%2022%20microphones%2C%20and%2010%20ultrasonic%20sensors.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMost%20notably%2C%20the%20car%20resembles%20Waymo's%20robotaxis%2C%20wearing%20a%20lidar%20on%20the%20roof%20like%20a%20hat.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe're%20a%20very%20sensor-heavy%20approach%2C%26quot%3B%20Fozzati%20said.%20%26quot%3BAll%20of%20these%20working%20together%20is%20very%2C%20very%20critical%20for%20scalability%20and%20for%20safety.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFozzati%20boasts%20that%20the%20car's%20self-driving%20system%20is%20powered%20by%20the%20%26quot%3Bworld's%20most%20powerful%20supercomputer%26quot%3B%20to%20be%20put%20inside%20a%20vehicle.%20The%20Robocar's%20brain%20is%20powered%20by%20Nvidia%20GPUs%20and%20can%20process%208%2C000%20trillion%20operations%20per%20second%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22788dd595-48bc-427d-bc6b-0b772d832ab8%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EA%20robot%20chauffeur%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ETensor's%20vision%20for%20Robocar's%20customer%20experience%20sounds%20like%20something%20from%20%26quot%3BThe%20Jetsons%26quot%3B%20or%20%26quot%3BI%2C%20Robot.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20car%20will%20be%20able%20to%20deliver%20itself%20to%20the%20owner%2C%20and%20if%20a%20service%20is%20required%20that's%20unrelated%20to%20the%20L4%20driving%20system%20%E2%80%94%20e.g.%2C%20a%20tire%20rotation%20%E2%80%94%20then%20the%20car%20can%20drive%20itself%20to%20the%20mechanic%20while%20the%20owner%20is%20at%20work.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%20the%20past%2C%20you've%20had%20to%20work%20for%20your%20car.%20Now%20the%20car%20is%20going%20to%20work%20for%20you%2C%26quot%3B%20Fozzati%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAmy%20Luca%2C%20Tensor's%20chief%20marketing%20officer%2C%20told%20BI%20that%20Tensor%20will%20also%20not%20collect%20data%20from%20its%20drivers%2C%20making%20safety%20and%20privacy%20some%20of%20the%20company's%20pillars.%20Companies%20like%20Tesla%20or%20Mobileye%20collect%20driving%20data%20from%20personally-owned%20cars%20to%20help%20train%20their%20driver-assistance%20systems.%20Tensor%20executives%20say%20they%20won't%20be%20doing%20that%20with%20Robocar%20unless%20owners%20provide%20permission.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20car%20has%20its%20own%20hard%20drive%2C%26quot%3B%20Luca%20said.%20%26quot%3BIt%20does%20not%20connect%20to%20a%20cloud.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%227184%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Tensor%20Robocar%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F68b3679ca17a8c5b4053ce44%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%225388%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ETensor%20Robocar%20is%20built%20with%20more%20than%20100%20sensors.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20Tensor%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ETesla%20says%20it%20has%20collected%20billions%20of%20miles%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Eof%20driving%20data%20to%20train%20an%20advanced%20driver%20assistance%20system%20(ADAS)%20that%20the%20company%20says%20will%20eventually%20become%20fully%20autonomous.%20Waymo%20says%20it%20now%20has%20more%20than%20100%20million%20autonomously%20driven%20miles%20under%