20with%20cousins%20who%20altered%20games%20so%20he%20could%20take%20part.%20He%20joined%20every%20conversation%2C%20every%20festival%2C%20every%20evening%20gathering%20under%20the%20stars.%20At%20home%2C%20inclusion%20wasn%E2%80%99t%20a%20philosophy.%20It%20was%20simply%20a%20way%20of%20life.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CMy%20parents%20never%20overprotected%20me%2C%20and%20they%20never%20neglected%20me%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%20%E2%80%9CThey%20treated%20me%20like%20they%20treated%20everyone%20else.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOutside%20the%20home%2C%20it%20was%20a%20different%20story.%20The%20local%20school%20refused%20to%20admit%20him.%20Teachers%20said%20they%20lacked%20the%20resources.%20So%20his%20parents%20did%20the%20only%20thing%20they%20could%20%E2%80%94%20they%20asked%20if%20he%20could%20at%20least%20sit%20in%20the%20classroom.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20was%20never%20officially%20enrolled.%20They%20never%20called%20my%20name%20during%20attendance.%20I%20just%20followed%20whichever%20class%20my%20neighbours%20were%20in%20and%20sat%20quietly%20at%20the%20back%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20recalls.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20500px)%20100vw%2C%20500px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F08%2Ffeatured-img-4_11zon-1756474544-500x262.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22500%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Despite%20barriers%20in%20mainstream%20education%2C%20Mahantesh%20went%20on%20to%20earn%20an%20MPhil%20and%20become%20a%20university%20lecturer.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F08%2Ffeatured-img-4_11zon-1756474544-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F08%2Ffeatured-img-4_11zon-1756474544-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F08%2Ffeatured-img-4_11zon-1756474544-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2