oft%20when%20wet%20but%20forms%20hard%20blocks%20when%20it%20gets%20dry.%20So%2C%20we%20need%20a%20sandy%20loamy%20solid%20that%20is%20well-drained.%20In%20our%20district%2C%20only%20a%20few%20blocks%20including%20our%20Kesla%20block%20have%20such%20soil%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETalking%20about%20the%20fertilisers%20and%20pesticides%20required%20for%20boosting%20turmeric%20growth%2C%20she%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CWe%20only%20use%20cow%20dung%20and%20%3Cem%3Ejeevamrut%20%3C%2Fem%3E(liquid%20organic%20manure)%20to%20boost%20the%20fertility%20of%20the%20soil.%20Besides%2C%20as%20turmeric%20in%20itself%20is%20antiseptic%20and%20herbal%2C%20there%20are%20fewer%20chances%20of%20pest%20attack.%20Even%20if%20pests%20attack%20the%20crop%2C%20we%20use%20Trichoderma%20biopesticides%20to%20control%20the%20attack%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20she%20wanted%20to%20be%20careful%20of%20growing%20a%20new%20crop%2C%20Kanchan%20sowed%20and%20used%20only%20an%20acre%20of%20land%20to%20sow%20eight%20quintals%20of%20turmeric%20root.%20After%20eight%20months%2C%20she%20harvested%20bumper%20produce%20of%20100%20quintals.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2FTurmeric-2-1711520044.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Last%20year%2C%20Kanchan%20got%20a%20bountiful%20harvest%20of%20400%20quintals%2C%20earning%20an%20income%20of%20Rs%2012%20lakh.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2FTurmeric-2-1711520044.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2FTurmeric-2-1711520044-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2FTurmeric-2-1711520044-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F